The paper discusses the security concerns in Smart Healthcare Systems (SHS) and proposes a machine learning-based security framework to detect malicious activities. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also extensively uses machine learning techniques, which makes cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) likely categories. The paper also focuses on the healthcare domain, which makes cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) a likely category. Finally, the paper deals with the integration of different devices in a system, which makes cs.SY (Systems and Control) a possible category.
